track.name: The Nurse Who Loved Me
comments: Love anything Maynard-y.  Also, I always get a visual of Paz slowly dancing around my bedroom in slinky lingerie...which never hurts a song's appeal ;)
least favorite, usually skip it. gad i'm not the only one.
how could you hate anything with Maynard? you're all insane...
A great cover, I love it when they keep the same melodic structure for a song; but then change everything else. Perfect.
Something about this song reminds me of Rasputina...

Can't get into this, no matter how much I try.
